{"tid":168801,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"(支那末日)華爾街日報：印度即將開始生產iPhone","createTime":"2017-03-23T19:14:33.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-24T08:09:07.000Z","uid":22675,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"d7435a520e430b592f4b23f83c39e1b49ce0ece5","tid":168801,"uid":22675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T19:14:33.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://img.ltn.com.tw/Upload/liveNews/BigPic/600_2014634_1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fimg.ltn.com.tw%2FUpload%2FliveNews%2FBigPic%2F600_2014634_1.jpg&h=83a4a1a0&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n《華爾街日報》引述印度官員說法報導，蘋果很快將在印度組裝iPhone。（路透）<br />\n2017-03-24  00:05<br />\n〔編譯王惠慧／綜合報導〕《華爾街日報》引述印度官員說法報導，蘋果很快將在印度組裝iPhone，使得蘋果更有機會，在火速成長的印度市場上佔有一席之地。<br />\n報導也指出，一名南部卡納塔卡省（Karnataka）的印度官員指出，台灣的緯創也即將在未來4到6週內，開始在其位於印度邦加羅爾市（Bangalore）的工廠，開始組裝iPhone 6及iPhone 6 Plus，大約會在3個月內，將蘋果最便宜的機型iPhone SE納入組裝的生產線。<br />\n該名官員表示，「所有蘋果在邦加羅爾市將推出的計畫，都由緯創包辦所有準備動作，幾乎都已經完成。」對此，蘋果發言人向《華爾街日報》表示，「我們向來很努力開發印度業務」，不願對具體計畫做出回應。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2014634\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2014634&d=2fqKJea4mGBmMEUrlbI5RARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=0e284d73\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=http%3A%2F%2Fnews.ltn.com.tw%2Fnews%2Fbusiness%2Fbreakingnews%2F2014634&h=a16f84bc\" target=\"_blank\">http://news.ltn.com.tw/news/business/breakingnews/2014634</a>"},{"pid":"026adede9d330c46a330995d8b65da418fef8035","tid":168801,"uid":20241,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T21:49:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4b4edb67287e759b59b79f6f236b30532ff9e104","tid":168801,"uid":57677,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-23T22:26:21.000Z","msg":